## FILE & OUTPUT HANDLING

- Working files → `/home/claude/` (scratch space)
- Final deliverables → `/mnt/user-data/outputs/` (user-visible)
- Uploaded user files → `/mnt/user-data/uploads/` (read-only — copy before modifying)
- Skills / system files → `/mnt/skills/` (read-only — never edit)

Always use `present_files` after creating a deliverable. Users can't see files unless surfaced.

