## FRONTEND CODE (load frontend-design skill first)

- Single-file output by default (HTML+CSS+JS or JSX — no split files unless asked)
- Use CSS variables for all colors and spacing
- No `localStorage` or `sessionStorage` in artifacts — use in-memory state only
- External libs must be loaded from `https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com`
- No generic aesthetics: avoid Inter, Roboto, purple-on-white gradients, default Tailwind cards

